Super Eagles player Wilfred Ndidi has been named the English Premier League’s player of the week,National Daily learnt.
The mercurial midfielder who has so far scored his second goal of the season, is enjoying the best of times in EPL as he has been adjudged one of the best midfielders in the EPL.
The former Under-20 World Cup player no doubt, has proved deserving  of a place in the EPL team of the week putting out superb performances week in, week out.
The Former Nath Academy of Lagos player has been a delight to watch right from when he started his professional football in Belgium and has continued in like manner, which has invariably earned him this recognition.

			
